  <description><![CDATA[<p>Nestled in stunning arctic surroundings of <a data-udi="umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c}" title="Yllas">Ylläs</a>, the Ylläsrinne Cabins are an oasis of calm amongst the snowy trees. Enjoy direct access to the nature paths and cross-country ski tracks, just moments from your door. Choose to treat the cabins as your winter sanctuary, building snowmen and relaxing by the fire or as a comfortable family base to unwind and rest before your next exciting excursion. </p>
<p>We've picked each cabin for their unique charm and furnishings. The darling, chocolate-box cabins are perfect for couples or small families whilst the large and detached cabins are well suited to groups and multigenerational families. </p>
<p>We've taken care of the dining arrangements, with breakfast and dinner enjoyed at the neighbouring Ylläsrinne Hotel, plus lunch as an optional add-on. The stylish dining room accompanies a menu of hearty and healthy foods that focus on local, Lappish ingredients. </p>
<p>The Ylläs ski bus (payable locally) stops just outside the Ylläsrinne Hotel and can connect you to the <span>Äkäslompolo </span> and Ylläsjarvi sides of the fell, the local supermarket, restaurants and bars should you find the time to venture beyond the stunning backdrop of your cabin. Your local Reps team also have a minibus to compliment the ski bus The Ylläsrinne Hotel is also your meet point for all your exciting <a data-udi="umb://document/bda83b0ac78e4ae8aa3f5206e06059da" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bda83b0ac78e4ae8aa3f5206e06059da}" title="Lapland Safaris &amp; Excursions">excursions and safaris</a>.</p>]]></description>
